name: Dododo Dwarf - Gogogo Glove
desc: During your Main Phase: You can Special Summon 1 "Zubaba" or "Gagaga" monster from your hand. While this card is in your GY, if you control a "Gogogo" or "Dododo" monster other than "Dododo Dwarf - Gogogo Glove": You can Special Summon this card, but banish it when it leaves the field. You can only use each effect of "Dododo Dwarf - Gogogo Glove" once per turn.
